snippet.title: Amber Heard Tarot Reading
snippet.description:
In this video, I ask the tarot card about Amber Heard. I also interpret Amber's star sign, read and give an interpretation of her aura.
Filmed: 16th May.

Edit: For the outcome, I meant to say soon or in the near future. I did not mean, within the next month. Ambers Sun sign is Taurus. I meant to say Libra is Amber's Moon sign, not rising sign.
It was not Amber Heard that won the libel case but News Group Newspapers Ltd.
